ng5-iu2, kiat sian7-ian5, kap pat8-lang5 u7 hou7-tong7, phou2-thong si5 hou7-siong tau3-saN-kang7, kian3-lip8 liong5-ho2 e5 jin5-che3 koan-he7, khip-siu che7-che7 e5 eng5-iong2 hun, chhiong-sit8 ka-ki7 e5 lai7-chai5, kam-goan7 cho3, hoaN-hi2 siu7. Na7 si7 tu2-tioh8 toa7-tiau5 e5 tai7-chi3, chiu7 u7 lang5 tau3 chi-oan5, tau3 kha-chhiu2, an2-ne lan2 tioh8 e7-tang3 hong5 hiong hoa3 kiat, sun7-li7 oan5-seng5 jim7-bu7. Sou2-i2 kong2 “hui7-kin” sui-jian5 chhian2, ma7 si7 e7-tang3 seng5-kong oan5-moa2. 
